<plot>A half hour religious drama series, airing on Sunday mornings on various networks and in syndication throughout the country. From 1952-1956 it featured stories of the Fisher Family. From 1956-1988 it began a single episode format that featured different casts each each week with stories that focused on religious and moral questions. It was one of the longest running shows on television (1952-1988).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?604863</url></doc>
